Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:14.98,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正粗雅宋_GBK\fad(100,0)\bord3\fax-0.3\fsp2\fs30\an1\c&H14172A&\3c&HE9EBEC&\b1\pos(935.29,826.86)\frz353.4}屬性：潛入
